                "correlation_property": null
              },
              "free_text": [
                " Mainly from the",
                " - measurement of deuteron fluence,",
                " - determination of radioactivities,",
                " - efficiency of Ge(Li) detector,",
                " - calculation for deuteron energy in each target foil,",
                " - inhomogeneity in the target.",
                "The uncertainties of relative measurement were also",
                " considered.",
                "The total uncertainty of cross sections was less than",
                " 6%, except for 197Au(d,2n)197gHg reaction at 12.7 MeV,",
                " for which the total uncertainty amounted to 7% due",
                " to the additional uncertainty resulting from the",
                " 197mHg decay."
              ]
